            span
            {
                line-height: 1in;
                border: 3px solid blue;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Test passes if the contest is contained within the blue borders and does not overlap.</p>
        <div>
            <span>Filler Text</span>
        </div>
